videos.description: Elijah Hughes rises high to reject Boston College's fast-break opportunity.
videos.headline: Hughes skies for violent block

videos.description: Buddy Boeheim swishes a pair of 3-pointers within a minute of each other late in the first half vs. Boston College.
videos.headline: Boeheim cooks Eagles from 3

videos.description: After Ky Bowman buries a 3-pointer, Syracuse's Tyus Battle takes it himself for a 3-point play at the other end.
videos.headline: Battle answers Bowman's one-man show at other end

videos.description: Ky Bowman buries another corner 3 as the Eagles make a late run in the Carrier Dome.
videos.headline: Bowman caps late 14-0 BC run
